					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"As we’re heading for the next hurdle, I explain more to Misaki as she finally started listening.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"在前往下一个关卡的途中，我对终于愿意放开心胸的美岬简单地说明了情况。",
